==========================

**Logistics Support Services for the Canadian Coast Guard Ship Sir Wilfrid Laurier**

## Tender Notice and Request for Standing Offer

The Department of Fisheries and Oceans/ Canadian Coast Guard invites interested suppliers to bid on a Request for Standing Offer (RFSO) for logistics support services. The services are required for the Canadian Coast Guard Ship Sir Wilfrid Laurier, which will operate in the high seas of the North Pacific Ocean off the coast of Japan from April to August.

## Key Details

*   **Tender Reference Number**: CB-353-28661140
*   **Solicitation Number**: 30005576
*   **Tender Closing Date**: April 12, 2024, at 1:00 p.m. EST
*   **Expected Contract Start Date**: April 10, 2024
*   **Expected Contract End Date**: March 31, 2029

## Background

The Department intend to establish a Standing Offer for logistics support services to provide logistical support for port visits. The services will be provided on an "as and when requested" basis. The requirement is subject to the provisions of the Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA).

## Selected Suppliers

The Department will select the successful supplier(s) based on the highest combined rating of technical merit and price. The Standing Offer will be issued to the Identified Users across Canada, excluding locations within Yukon, Northwest Territories, Nunavut, Quebec, and Labrador that are subject to Comprehensive Land Claims Agreements (CLCAs).

## Relevant Attachments

To access the tender documents, please visit the Canada Buys website using the following links:

*   [PDF Document 1](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/33940/30005576---solicitation-addendum-1--addenda-1---bilingual_.pdf)
*   [PDF Document 2](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/33940/30005576---solicitation-addendum-2--addenda-2---bilingual.pdf)
*   [RFSA Document](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/33940/30005576---rfso.pdf)

For any questions or concerns regarding this tender notice, please contact:

*   **Name:** Pascal Busungu
*   **Email:** pascal.busungu
